#

Pesto Tomato Toast

10 min
$4.5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Description

A delightful blend of toasted bread, fresh tomatoes, and a savory spread that captures the essence of summer in every bite.

Ingredients

  • bread: 2 slices
  • tomatoes: 1 medium, sliced
  • parmesan cheese: 2 tablespoons, grated
  • basil pesto: 2 tablespoons
